org.apache.hcatalog.templeton.tool
Class HDFSStorage

Object
  HDFSStorage
All Implemented Interfaces:
TempletonStorage
public class HDFSStorage
extends Object
implements TempletonStorage

HDFS implementation of templeton storage. This implementation assumes that all keys in key/value pairs are chosen such that they don't have any newlines in them.

Description copied from interface: TempletonStorage
Get all the name/value pairs stored for this id. Be careful using getFields() -- optimistic locking will mean that your odds of a conflict are decreased if you read/write one field at a time. getFields() is intended for read-only usage. If the type is UNKNOWN, search for the id in all types.
